        <div class="intro">
            <h2 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 15px;">Need Help?</h2>
            <p>Find answers to common questions below, or contact us directly!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>üìö Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I play Neo Run?</h3>
                <p>It's simple!</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Tap</strong> to jump</li>
                    <li><strong>Double-tap</strong> for double jump</li>
                    <li><strong>Triple-tap</strong> for triple jump</li>
                    <li>Avoid obstacles and collect coins!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I unlock new skins?</h3>
                <p>
                    Collect coins during gameplay and use them to purchase skins in the Shop. 
                    You can also earn coins by completing daily missions or purchasing coin packs.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What are daily missions?</h3>
                <p>
                    Daily missions refresh every 24 hours and give you specific challenges to complete. 
                    Finish missions to earn extra coins and XP! Check the Missions tab to see your current tasks.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How does the level system work?</h3>
                <p>
                    As you play, you earn XP based on your performance. Collect more coins, build combos, 
                    and survive longer to earn more XP. Level up to unlock new content and features!
                </p>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>üí° Tip:</strong> VIP Pass gives you 2x XP to level up faster!
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What are power-ups and how do I use them?</h3>
                <p>Power-ups give you special abilities during gameplay:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Speed Boost:</strong> Run faster temporarily</li>
                    <li><strong>Shield:</strong> Protect yourself from one obstacle</li>
                    <li><strong>Magnet:</strong> Auto-collect nearby coins</li>
                    <li><strong>2x Coins:</strong> Double coin collection (VIP perk)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Activate power-ups from the shop before starting a run!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do in-app purchases work?</h3>
                <p>
                    Neo Run is free to play! In-app purchases are optional and include:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Coin packs to unlock skins faster</li>
                    <li>VIP Pass for 2x XP and exclusive benefits</li>
                    <li>Extra lives to continue your run</li>
                    <li>Remove ads for uninterrupted gameplay</li>
                </ul>
                <p>All purchases are processed securely through Apple.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>I made a purchase but didn't receive my items</h3>
                <p>Try these steps:</p>
                <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Close and restart the app</li>
                    <li>Check your purchase history in the App Store</li>
                    <li>Go to Settings ‚Üí Restore Purchases in the game</li>
                    <li>Make sure you're connected to the internet</li>
                </ol>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    Still having issues? Contact us with your receipt and we'll help!
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>My game progress was lost. Can I recover it?</h3>
                <p>
                    If you enabled iCloud sync, your progress should automatically restore when you 
                    reinstall the app on the same Apple ID account.
                </p>
                <p><strong>To enable iCloud sync:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>iOS Settings ‚Üí [Your Name] ‚Üí iCloud</li>
                    <li>Make sure "Neo Run" is enabled</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Local data is lost if you delete the app without iCloud sync enabled.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>The game is lagging or crashing</h3>
                <p>Try these solutions:</p>
                <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li><strong>Restart the app</strong> - Close completely and reopen</li>
                    <li><strong>Restart your device</strong> - Turn it off and on</li>
                    <li><strong>Update the app</strong> - Check for updates in the App Store</li>
                    <li><strong>Update iOS</strong> - Make sure you're running the latest iOS version</li>
                    <li><strong>Free up storage</strong> - Delete unused apps or photos</li>
                    <li><strong>Close background apps</strong> - Double-click home and swipe up</li>
                </ol>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    Still experiencing issues? Contact us with your device model and iOS version.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I restore purchases on a new device?</h3>
                <p>
                    All your purchases are linked to your Apple ID and can be restored for free:
                </p>
                <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Download Neo Run on your new device</li>
                    <li>Sign in with the same Apple ID you used for purchases</li>
                    <li>Open the game and go to Settings</li>
                    <li>Tap "Restore Purchases"</li>
                    <li>Your purchases will be restored!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I play offline?</h3>
                <p>
                    Yes! Neo Run works completely offline. You don't need an internet connection 
                    to play. However, you'll need internet to:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Make in-app purchases</li>
                    <li>Sync progress with iCloud</li>
                    <li>Update the app</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I delete my game data?</h3>
                <p>To reset your progress:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>In-game:</strong> Settings ‚Üí Reset Progress</li>
                    <li><strong>Complete removal:</strong> Delete the Neo Run app from your device</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Warning:</strong> This action cannot be undone!
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Is Neo Run safe for children?</h3>
                <p>
                    Yes! Neo Run is rated 4+ and appropriate for all ages. The game features:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>‚úÖ No violence or inappropriate content</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ No online multiplayer or chat</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ No collection of personal information</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ No third-party advertising</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ Family-friendly gameplay</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>Parents:</strong> You can restrict in-app purchases using iOS Parental Controls.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How do I request a refund?</h3>
                <p>
                    All purchases are processed by Apple. To request a refund:
                </p>
                <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Go to <strong>reportaproblem.apple.com</strong></li>
                    <li>Sign in with your Apple ID</li>
                    <li>Find your Neo Run purchase</li>
                    <li>Click "Report a Problem"</li>
                    <li>Select "Request a refund"</li>
                    <li>Choose a reason and submit</li>
                </ol>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    Apple usually responds within 48 hours.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
